Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:01.50,0:00:02.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,成功了，英麥曼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:03.33,0:00:05.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,曉得我的厲害了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:07.47,0:00:11.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,過生日喔，好開心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:11.34,0:00:15.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,出生然後回歸大地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.68,0:00:18.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,祝福你，祝福你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:18.21,0:00:21.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,生日快樂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:21.12,0:00:24.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,親愛的迪奧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:32.66,0:00:35.89,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,just keep on trying, keep on flying\N{\c&HFFBF00&}just keep on trying, keep on flying
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:35.96,0:00:38.86,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,I will be the light\N{\c&HFFBF00&}I will be the light
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:39.70,0:00:46.37,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,如果說把黎明　當作是一個開始\N{\c&HFFBF00&}夜明けをひと　つの始まりとするなら
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:46.97,0:00:53.54,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,如果說現在就是來臨的時刻\N{\c&HFFBF00&}今が来るべき時だとするなら
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:54.01,0:00:58.58,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,與你的煙雲時代交響曲 飛向雲海的彼端 \N{\c&HFFBF00&}君とのCloud Age Symphony  雲の海の向こうに
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:58.65,0:01:07.19,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,飛往光芒照射的方向\N{\c&HFFBF00&}光が射す方へ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:09.63,0:01:22.87,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah～是否可以遇見有如魔法的那瞬間？\N{\c&HFFBF00&}Ah～魔法のような一瞬に会えるのか？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:22.94,0:01:37.38,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,取代寒冷的黑夜  我倆展翅飛翔\N{\c&HFFBF00&}冷たい夜を引き替えに  二人は羽ばたいて
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:37.46,0:01:46.30,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,在那盡頭  抓住了永恆…\N{\c&HFFBF00&}永远を掴む、その果てには
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:59.68,0:02:01.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剛剛那個急俯衝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:01.22,0:02:04.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要我倆聯手\N沒有什麼可以難倒我們的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:04.35,0:02:06.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是曉得EXILE被人搶走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:06.35,0:02:08.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,戴芬妮一定會氣炸了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:08.66,0:02:09.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:09.86,0:02:12.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艦橋那邊沒有回應
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.43,0:02:13.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,應該是故障吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:13.86,0:02:18.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們的船\N不是常常會發生這種事情嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:18.13,0:02:20.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,銀之戰艦，這裡是五號機
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:22.70,0:02:25.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會不會是剛才衝太猛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.31,0:02:27.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以才斷線了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:29.21,0:02:34.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H8dccf0&}迪奧的城堡\NRook Dio
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.26,0:02:46.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都沒人在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.86,0:02:48.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好寂寞哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.26,0:02:50.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明明是英雄凱旋歸來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.26,0:02:51.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,居然都沒人來迎接
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.03,0:02:53.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到底怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.63,0:02:56.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是不是正在慶祝找到EXILE了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.60,0:02:58.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,連葛溫他們也是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.04,0:03:01.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為大家都喜歡熱鬧嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.98,0:03:03.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們也快過去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.48,0:03:07.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一號機已經回來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.88,0:03:09.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看來她們也沒事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.78,0:03:12.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拉薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.59,0:03:14.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾兒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.52,0:03:15.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,魯修拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.83,0:03:23.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.56,0:03:25.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是艾兒做的夢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.50,0:03:32.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾兒的…夢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.24,0:03:37.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道他們在開作戰會議嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.01,0:03:41.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,八成是在準備\N把艾兒帶到EXILE上…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.98,0:03:45.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.29,0:03:47.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們去找找看吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.82,0:03:51.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這簡直就像是幽靈船
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.09,0:03:55.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,據說大風暴區裡\N有時會出現這種漂流船
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.53,0:03:58.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,船上一個人都沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.87,0:04:01.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吃到一半的食物\N和看到一半的書
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.20,0:04:04.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,處處都留著\N剛才還有人在的痕跡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.98,0:04:10.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有人說那是被EXILE給吃掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.84,0:04:14.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過那充其量\N也只是虛構的故事罷了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.02,0:04:19.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那裡好像有人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.59,0:04:20.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去看看吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.17,0:04:37.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拉薇和艾兒都不在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.54,0:04:39.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不要一副那麼嚴肅的樣子嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.87,0:04:41.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們一定是想嚇我們一跳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.84,0:04:43.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,躲到什麼地方去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.65,0:04:52.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會完全沒有人跡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.09,0:04:53.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這有點不對勁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.29,0:04:57.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拉薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.49,0:04:59.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾兒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.43,0:05:07.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看來剛剛還有人在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.31,0:05:12.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,酒？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.44,0:05:14.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是血
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.28,0:05:16.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,血…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.01,0:05:21.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們去艦橋看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.28,0:05:25.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果連艦橋都沒人的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.29,0:05:27.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那可就是貨真價實的幽靈船了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.37,0:05:43.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啦，原來你們都在嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.51,0:05:47.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克勞士‧沃卡歸艦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.17,0:05:48.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們都怎麼了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.98,0:05:50.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,船上怎麼連一個人…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.44,0:05:51.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我等你很久了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.05,0:05:53.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,迪奧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.25,0:05:57.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你都到哪兒去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.42,0:05:59.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,迪奧，她是誰啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.25,0:06:01.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.56,0:06:04.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,迪奧他是高興得說不出話來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.96,0:06:08.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克勞士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.83,0:06:09.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.53,0:06:10.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾兒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.17,0:06:13.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這位是戴芬妮總帥陛下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.93,0:06:16.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不許無禮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.37,0:06:17.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳就是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.70,0:06:21.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為你遲遲不回來\N我只好來接你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.54,0:06:24.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳是用什麼方法到這裡來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.11,0:06:26.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想到哪裡隨時就能到哪裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.65,0:06:29.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為這世界是屬於我的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.55,0:06:31.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你說是吧，希卡達
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.69,0:06:33.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的，陛下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.79,0:06:36.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,包括這艘船也是屬於我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.59,0:06:38.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對吧，魯修拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.19,0:06:39.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.43,0:06:40.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,魯修拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.70,0:06:48.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好一陣沒見\N你長大了不少嘛，迪奧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.10,0:06:51.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我很高興
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.51,0:06:53.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這人是你的隨從嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.64,0:06:54.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.74,0:06:57.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那…難道是你朋友嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.14,0:06:59.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我…和迪奧是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.98,0:07:03.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,迪奧這還是頭一次交到朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.62,0:07:07.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對了，帶他到基爾特來玩嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.42,0:07:09.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不可以，他…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.99,0:07:15.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你願意接受我的招待吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.26,0:07:18.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希卡達
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.27,0:07:19.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.47,0:07:24.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這艘船的艦長\N怎麼還不出來打招呼呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.40,0:07:26.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,十分抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.14,0:07:29.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拘捕所有船員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.28,0:07:30.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.51,0:07:32.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,目前正在搜索艦內
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.61,0:07:34.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,停機庫裡的人已全被拘捕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.78,0:07:36.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有任何異常狀況
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.02,0:07:39.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,出發吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.02,0:07:44.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希卡達你留下來\N把曉得關鍵謎詩的人找出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.19,0:07:44.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.99,0:07:47.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可別一時情急殺了人家哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.09,0:07:50.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,之後還得交給審問官呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.33,0:07:53.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,迪奧殿下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.33,0:07:55.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,迪奧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.08,0:08:04.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,停機庫中有克勞地亞反應
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.45,0:08:07.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,佛米加，快回答
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.71,0:08:09.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,佛米加？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.35,0:08:14.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,起飛同時，把動力開到最大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.72,0:08:15.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.02,0:08:46.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,達格貝…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.95,0:08:48.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,撤退
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.36,0:08:52.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,戴芬妮來了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.83,0:08:56.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳不需要害怕，艾兒‧薇絲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.93,0:08:59.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是個可愛的孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.57,0:09:02.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,撫養妳長大的漢彌爾敦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.14,0:09:05.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我從以前就很熟呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.07,0:09:06.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳是說爺爺嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.24,0:09:09.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為她一直都想殺了人家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.94,0:09:12.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,迪奧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.18,0:09:14.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我很難過喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.38,0:09:17.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為你都不肯回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.28,0:09:18.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.59,0:09:19.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,迪奧…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.72,0:09:21.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過我一直相信你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.52,0:09:22.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為我們艾拉克萊家的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.99,0:09:27.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是不可能不出席宣誓儀式的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.94,0:10:10.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艦長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.07,0:10:12.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亞力克斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.92,0:10:25.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,發生緊急狀況
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.45,0:10:27.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是銀之戰艦所屬\N大型貨櫃先鋒艇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.82,0:10:29.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請求著艦許可
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.02,0:10:31.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,文生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.83,0:10:34.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,銀之戰艦被基爾特…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.16,0:10:35.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,陛下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.50,0:10:38.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快讓貨櫃機上來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.50,0:10:40.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們要飛離銀之戰艦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.43,0:10:41.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.40,0:10:47.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你這艦長還真是不懂禮貌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.44,0:10:52.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過這也替我省下了\N找你的工夫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.81,0:10:55.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,告訴我關鍵謎詩吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.32,0:10:57.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你應該知道的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.12,0:11:00.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為在那個沒品的\N賈卡羅的拍賣會上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.12,0:11:04.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,偷走了漢彌爾敦家謎詩的人\N就是你不是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.49,0:11:08.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,收集古詩是我的興趣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.66,0:11:11.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是當小偷就不對了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.93,0:11:13.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,告訴妳是可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.40,0:11:15.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過我有一個條件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.24,0:11:20.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,居然敢和我做交易\N你這人還真有意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.64,0:11:23.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不准對銀之戰艦出手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.68,0:11:26.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就要看你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.71,0:11:29.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在天空的彼方存在的是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.48,0:11:34.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那不是我們家的謎詩嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.76,0:11:40.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這表示四句你全都知道了對吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.93,0:11:44.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說要得到EXILE\N只有靠我了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.00,0:11:48.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是個壞心眼的大叔啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.44,0:11:52.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放了那孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.47,0:11:54.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你真傻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.21,0:11:56.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾兒‧薇絲可是屬於我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.28,0:12:00.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為你看她這麼可愛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.61,0:12:02.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,況且如果沒有這孩子的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.72,0:12:05.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好不容易到手的詩\N也派不上用場
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.39,0:12:06.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把艾兒…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.49,0:12:07.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不要說話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.16,0:12:13.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們走吧，迪奧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.53,0:12:15.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,宣誓儀式就要開始了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.96,0:12:19.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真拿你這孩子沒辦法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.73,0:12:20.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,魯修拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.77,0:12:22.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.37,0:12:24.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請恕我無禮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.51,0:12:27.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,魯修拉，住手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.21,0:12:30.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜託你，請你不要妄動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:30.08,0:12:31.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,魯修拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.38,0:12:33.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,反抗戴芬妮陛下是沒用的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.01,0:12:36.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不是迪奧的朋友嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.72,0:12:39.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們身分不同
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.09,0:12:40.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,魯修拉…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.25,0:12:43.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了，不需要再待在這船上了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.42,0:12:46.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希卡達，把客人帶到基爾特去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.66,0:12:48.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,屬下遵命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.80,0:12:49.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,迪奧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.10,0:12:52.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克勞士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.27,0:12:53.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾兒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.84,0:12:58.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把艾兒放開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.81,0:13:02.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係，隨他們去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.04,0:13:06.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去把小船準備好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.08,0:13:07.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,遵命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.51,0:13:08.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.82,0:13:11.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克勞士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.89,0:13:13.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拉薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.19,0:13:14.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳還好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.35,0:13:16.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我沒事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.26,0:13:19.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用擔心，我一定會回來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.00,0:13:23.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希卡達
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.23,0:13:23.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.36,0:13:26.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這下所有的東西都齊全了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.60,0:13:28.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去確保住EXILE
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.50,0:13:30.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,屬下遵命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.24,0:13:36.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克勞士…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.54,0:13:37.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艦長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.68,0:13:38.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艦長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.61,0:13:39.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艦長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.42,0:13:44.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.15,0:13:48.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我絕對會回來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.76,0:13:52.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,回來保護拉薇妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.56,0:13:54.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等，克勞士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.10,0:13:57.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克勞士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.14,0:14:09.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拉薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.82,0:14:24.12,OD,,0000,0000,0000,,不要放棄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.83,0:14:31.56,OD,,0000,0000,0000,,在這個邊界的小鎮上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.63,0:14:38.13,OD,,0000,0000,0000,,我們出生長大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.20,0:14:43.44,OD,,0000,0000,0000,,爸媽曾經教給我們的勇氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.51,0:14:49.51,OD,,0000,0000,0000,,千萬不要忘記
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.98,0:14:55.89,OD,,0000,0000,0000,,當你受傷的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.96,0:15:01.55,OD,,0000,0000,0000,,當你迷失的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:01.63,0:15:06.93,OD,,0000,0000,0000,,當徘徊在這片黑暗裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:07.00,0:15:13.46,OD,,0000,0000,0000,,當獨自在孤獨的風裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.94,0:15:19.31,OD,,0000,0000,0000,,請不要放棄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.38,0:15:21.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,終於就是明天了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:21.51,0:15:24.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼我們會生在這種世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.32,0:15:29.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真希望能生在一個\N不會餓著不會凍著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.19,0:15:32.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也不會被大砲打到的世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.56,0:15:35.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我會保護
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.03,0:15:39.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我會保護妳的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.70,0:15:42.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明明就做不到的說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:51.68,0:15:53.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這可以讓您心情放鬆一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.42,0:15:59.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亞力克斯那小子太大意了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.15,0:16:02.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,您不用擔心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.89,0:16:07.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我文生‧亞傑一定會把\N銀之戰艦上的船員救出來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.13,0:16:10.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒事啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.26,0:16:13.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那小子沒那麼容易就死的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.26,0:16:39.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別擔心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.06,0:16:41.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有我在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.26,0:16:46.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們是客人，儘管放輕鬆點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.73,0:16:48.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,迪奧呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.33,0:16:51.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有很多事要準備，很麻煩的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.67,0:16:55.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明天是那孩子\N長大成人的重要日子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.11,0:16:57.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們也會一起幫他慶祝吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.18,0:17:01.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對了\N我帶你們參觀一下城裡吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:01.85,0:17:03.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.92,0:17:06.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道什麼是組件吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.29,0:17:09.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這正是基爾特公會\N給地上的人們恩惠的證明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.02,0:17:11.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果沒有這個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.29,0:17:14.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們就只能爬在地上過日子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:19.80,0:17:23.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請看\N這裡就是舉行宣誓儀式的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.70,0:17:25.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,宣誓儀式？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.64,0:17:30.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是孩子們長大成人\N必須經歷的成人儀式考驗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.28,0:17:31.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,成人儀式？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.01,0:17:36.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很漂亮吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.28,0:17:41.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我最喜歡漂亮和可愛的東西了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.16,0:17:45.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,薔薇真的很棒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:45.36,0:17:49.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不只外表美麗，還有各種用處
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:49.56,0:17:51.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們餓了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.23,0:17:53.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,晚餐應該已經準備好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.50,0:17:56.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過你們那身衣服\N可真讓人受不了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.04,0:17:58.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,得換掉才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:58.71,0:17:59.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,魯修拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:59.81,0:18:00.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.51,0:18:04.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放開我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:04.64,0:18:06.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我叫你們放開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.61,0:18:08.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,迪奧殿下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.85,0:18:15.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.69,0:18:17.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是規定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.09,0:18:24.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我…\N我想保持自己現在這個樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:24.13,0:18:25.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放開我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.40,0:18:28.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,求求你，希卡達
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.64,0:18:30.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,住手啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.14,0:18:33.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,魯修拉，叫魯修拉過來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.07,0:18:35.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,魯修拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.93,0:18:54.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎喲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.43,0:18:56.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,兩人都很合身嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.00,0:19:00.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來，快坐下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:05.14,0:19:07.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用客氣，快吃吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:08.21,0:19:12.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是只有在有頂級水的地方\N才能採收到的蘑菇做的沙拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:14.28,0:19:16.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要不要吃吃看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:16.85,0:19:18.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請問…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.52,0:19:20.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.15,0:19:23.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,迪奧和亞力克斯呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.32,0:19:27.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們…不一起來吃嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:27.76,0:19:30.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用餐的時候\N請把注意力放在菜餚上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:30.26,0:19:31.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是禮貌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.20,0:19:33.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要怕，艾兒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.77,0:19:36.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別擔心，有我在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:47.88,0:19:49.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,捕捉到動力音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:49.22,0:19:50.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是基爾特艦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:50.48,0:19:52.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然還是來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:52.52,0:19:54.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,左舷，距離五哩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.22,0:19:55.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全速倒退
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:55.59,0:19:56.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,逃進雲堆裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.06,0:19:58.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全速倒退
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:58.59,0:20:00.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你沒事吧，雷修斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.43,0:20:03.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒事，組件運轉也很順暢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:09.40,0:20:11.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,基爾特艦朝我們開火了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:11.54,0:20:12.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,左舵打滿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:24.88,0:20:27.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是在度西斯的冰河捕獲的\N犛牛做的牛排
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:28.76,0:20:33.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽說每捉一頭牛\N都得要凍死一堆人呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:33.23,0:20:34.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很棒吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:36.46,0:20:39.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,至少讓艾兒回去好嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:39.47,0:20:43.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今年的生日週\N對迪奧來說很特別
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:43.84,0:20:46.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你們是他朋友的話\N就陪他一起過吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:50.14,0:20:54.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這麼出色的菜餚\N你們還是頭一次看到吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:57.92,0:20:59.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是醋漬沼魚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:00.29,0:21:01.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為了洗掉它身上的泥巴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:01.35,0:21:03.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是要用掉\N100加侖的頂級水呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:06.13,0:21:08.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不合你們的口味嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:08.73,0:21:11.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,竟然把頂級水用在這種地方…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:11.43,0:21:13.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:13.23,0:21:16.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在下面大家都只能喝著髒水
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:16.57,0:21:19.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,努力設法要活下去，妳卻…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:21.11,0:21:22.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你太不成熟了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:22.88,0:21:27.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個世界太小了\N小得只能養得活一小搓的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:27.18,0:21:28.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你明白嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:28.41,0:21:32.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是隨你們高興吃喝玩樂下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:32.82,0:21:34.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這世界沒多久就會毀滅了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:34.95,0:21:37.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我才要代表大家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:37.49,0:21:40.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來享受這極致的快樂啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:42.73,0:21:45.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對小孩子來說或許太難懂了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:45.53,0:21:46.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,準備好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:48.00,0:21:49.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,迪奧已經打扮好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:54.71,0:21:55.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,迪奧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:55.81,0:21:57.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:01.88,0:22:03.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,迪奧…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:03.45,0:22:06.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們看看\N他這威風凜凜的表情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:06.45,0:22:10.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這下迪奧也成了\N可以獨當一面的基爾特人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:10.09,0:22:12.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的，姊姊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:13.36,0:22:14.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,迪奧…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:36.22,0:22:40.05,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,黑夜的時光逐漸逼近\N{\c&HFFBF00&}夜の時間が迫り来る
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:41.95,0:22:47.59,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,你離我如此接近感覺  卻好遠…\N{\c&HFFBF00&}あなたはこんな近く でも遠い…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:47.66,0:22:52.46,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,你的憧憬是什麼\N{\c&HFFBF00&}何に憧れて
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:52.53,0:22:58.20,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,心中想的又是誰\N{\c&HFFBF00&}だれを想うのか
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:58.27,0:23:03.83,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,你奮不顧身的身影\N{\c&HFFBF00&}いのち賭ける姿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:03.91,0:23:12.65,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,有一種透明的美麗  令我噤聲無言\N{\c&HFFBF00&}透き通る美しさに 言葉を飲んだ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:12.72,0:23:18.45,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你欲飛往天際\N{\c&HFFBF00&}あなたが空を行くなら
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:18.52,0:23:24.46,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,我願成為你的翅膀\N{\c&HFFBF00&}わたしは翼になりたい
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:24.53,0:23:30.73,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,無論風有多麼強\N{\c&HFFBF00&}どんなに強い風にも
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:30.80,0:23:36.04,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,也永遠不會折斷的柔婉翅膀\N{\c&HFFBF00&}けして折れない しなやかな羽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:36.11,0:23:48.25,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,相信有一天  我會擁有那樣一對翅膀\N{\c&HFFBF00&}いつか　きっと持つから
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:51.59,0:23:52.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（下回預告）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:52.83,0:23:56.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,臉上刻有宣誓的印記的\N未來領袖們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:56.63,0:23:58.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,若想繼承我的名號
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:58.90,0:24:01.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就拿起這把宣誓之劍吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:01.87,0:24:05.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道迪奧他\N為什麼那麼怕妳了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:05.47,0:24:08.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為妳打算抹殺迪奧他的心
